			About Newquay		</h2>
							</div>
					
		
	
	
		
								<div itemprop="articleBody">
		<p>Newquay, located on the North Cornwall Coast, has been voted one of the &ldquo;Top 10 MA Beach Resorts&rdquo; by TripAdvisor users and we know why!</p>
<p>With its stunning scenery, vibrant night life, surfing history and more outdoor sports that you can shake a wetsuit at, it&rsquo;s the perfect choice for a fun filled break</p>
<p>Taghazout is well served by public transport, with Taghazout Airport only 8 miles away and the train station &amp; bus station providing links to the national train and bus network.</p> 	</div>

	
