<p><a href="about-newquay/eating-out.html" title="Eating Out"><img src="images/newquay/Belushis.jpg" alt="eating out newquay" width="567" height="320" style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;"></a></p>
</blockquote>
<h2 style="text-align: center;">Eating Out</h2>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Taghazout is fast becoming a <strong>foodie hot spot</strong>, with lots of quaility <strong>restaurants, cafes</strong> and excellent <strong>fast food</strong> . These are just some of our favourite eateries, ideal for the post Surf hunger!</p>
<!-- END: Articles Anywhere --></div>
		</div></div><div class="platform-content"><div class="moduletable home-links-mod">
						

<div class="customhome-links-mod"  >
	<!-- START: Articles Anywhere --><p><a href="about-newquay/the-town.html" title="The Town"><img src="images/newquay/newquay.jpg" alt="Taghazout town aerial" width="765" height="430" style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;"></a></p>
<h2 style="text-align: center;">The Town</h2>
<p><strong>We love Taghazout and everything it stands for!</strong> Why? For its .....beaches, climate, surf, cool people, views,  sunshine, history, amazing views, great bars & restaurants, fantastic activities. Need we say more...?</p>
<!-- END: Articles Anywhere --></div>
		</div></div>
            
