<div class="customhome-links-mod"  >
	<!-- START: Articles Anywhere --><p><a href="about-newquay/the-beaches.html" title="The Beaches"><img src="images/newquay/Beaches.jpg" alt="surfing Taghazout beaches cornwall" width="738" height="415" style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;"></a></p>
<h2 style="text-align: center;">The Beaches</h2>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Taghazout has 9 (yes, thats 9!) beaches</strong>, each offering a different experience and vibe, as well as very different surf conditions.  Check out our <strong>insiders guide</strong> to the to find your perfect sandy haven!</p>
<!-- END: Articles Anywhere --></div>
		</div></div><div class="platform-content"><div class="moduletable home-links-mod">
						

<div class="customhome-links-mod"  >
	<!-- START: Articles Anywhere --><p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 1.5em;"><img src="images/Other&#32;activities/OTHER&#32;(1).jpg" alt="OTHER (1)"></span></strong></p>
<h2 style="text-align: center;">Other Activities</h2>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 1.5em;"></span>Taghazout is not just about the surfing (although it is the most important activity in our opinion!!) there are loads of other activities available, including <strong>SUP</strong>, <strong>Coasteering</strong>, <strong>Fishing, Kayaking</strong> and More!</p>
<!-- END: Articles Anywhere --></div>
