<h2 style="text-align: center;">BoardMasters</h2>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Taghazout has a one of a kind<strong> music festival</strong> that takes place in August every year. Think live music, surf and spectacular sunsets! Argana Surf School are a <strong>proud supporter</strong> and partner of Boardmasters! </p>
