<h2 style="text-align: center;">Pubs & Bars</h2>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Taghazout is famous for its nightlife, with <strong>lots of bars and pubs </strong>offering the party goer all they could ever want! Check out our<strong> guide to the Pubs and bars </strong>to ensure the best Apres Surf Fun!</p>
